body:
Fixes #40660
Fixes #37437

### Description

This PR fixes the 2 issue above. For #37437, I fix it so that dashboards return `fit` event correctly.

### How to verify

1. Follow the repro steps in #40660
1. For #37437, subscribe to `message` event. I use this custom snippet for interactive embedding to change the embedding height. When the height is 0, it uses the default height instead.
    ```ts
    useEffect(() => {
      const callback = (event) => {
        const metabaseEvent = event.data.metabase
        if (metabaseEvent) {
          if (
            metabaseEvent.type === 'location' &&
            !metabaseEvent.location.pathname.startsWith('/dashboard/')
          ) {
            setHeight(0)
          }
          if (metabaseEvent.type === 'frame') {
            setHeight(metabaseEvent.frame.height)
          }
        }
      }
      window.addEventListener('message', callback)
      return () => {
        window.removeEventListener('message', callback)
      }
    }, [])
    ```
